    "description": "BroadBand Tower, Inc. provides computer and media solutions platforms in Japan. It operates in two segments, Computer Platform Business and Media Solutions Business. The Computer Platform Business segment engages in the lease of real estate for data centers and installation of data center facilities; operation, maintenance support, construction of multi-cloud environments, MSP monitoring and operation services, and SaaS-based security solutions; provision of maintenance services for storage devices and related software products; and development and sale of information leakage prevention software products. Its Media Solutions Business segment includes content platform, a multi-channel program and in-house channel distribution service for cable TV operators; and information platform, a data broadcasting distribution service for community channels for cable TV operators and regional disaster prevention services for local governments. The company also offers JC-HITS, a multichannel broadcast streaming platform service for regional cable TV providers, and JC-DATA, a data broadcasting service. BroadBand Tower, Inc. was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
